Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼 七海怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道 好像在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師 青山她好像身體不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我帶她去保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走吧 青山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經沒事了 神田就先回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那 如果有什麼事要叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}絕對要叫我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您好 我是神田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}辛苦了 我是藤澤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}標題審查會已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常遺憾 本次未能通過…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田同學 神田同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事實上 在提交給標題審查會的眾多策劃之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有另一款音律遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}詳細的內容無法說明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是一款使用了以歌為題材的人氣動畫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以及現今網路上流行的VOCALOID樂曲的策劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然是沿襲了以往音律遊戲的十分簡單的設計
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但本次是那款遊戲通過了審查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是說音律遊戲不需要兩款嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 最大的理由就在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼會… 這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我能將碰頭會的時間提前一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓你能早些提交給標題審查會的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我很感激藤澤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}禮拜六明明是假日 還為我擠出時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}託您的福 我才能精推細磨出策劃書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我受益良多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不用說這些「明事理」的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己的未來 在自己力不可及的地方就決定了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論再怎麼努力 仍有無法改變的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是不合理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不必這樣輕易認同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.19,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 社會上像這樣不合理的事四處皆是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}日後我會再詳細跟你報告標題審查會的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有什麼現在想問的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本次的策劃 藤澤先生您有何評價
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請務必告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}作為遊戲製作者而言 真想做個試玩版出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}作為玩家而言 希望自己能有機會玩一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根據手感 可能會是很有趣的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倘若平衡調整出錯 也可能會成為乏味的糞作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常感謝 感覺稍微輕鬆了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 以後再聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這還真是…難熬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.19,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}另一款音律遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那種事不是無可奈何的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是要我怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是難以忍受啊 這種結局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs28\shad0\bord0\c&H555B68&\frz23.02\pos(644.001,355.667)\frx4\fry6}馬尾辮的情況如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs28\shad0\bord0\c&H3A4254&\frz23.02\frx4\fry6\pos(630.667,406.333)}她說已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs28\shad0\bord0\c&H3A4254&\frz23.02\frx4\fry6\pos(693.334,418.333)}就讓她在保健室睡一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs28\shad0\bord0\c&H3A4254&\frz23.02\frx4\fry6\pos(630.667,406.333)}她說已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs28\shad0\bord0\c&H3A4254&\frz23.02\frx4\fry6\pos(693.334,418.333)}就讓她在保健室睡一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:05.20,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\shad0\c&H7D7B94&\3c&HADDDDC&\frz40.64\pos(940.001,445.001)}神田你是白痴嗎。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:05.20,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\shad0\c&H7D7B94&\3c&HADDDDC&\frz40.64\pos(938.663,545.002)}沒什麼事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.20,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\shad0\c&H7D7B94&\3c&HADDDDC&\frz40.64\pos(1030.66,563.668)}怎麼會哭成那樣。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯 正如你所言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經夠了 已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山為了櫻花莊 為了真白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了美{\fnＦＡ 丸ゴシックＭ\fs42}咲{\r\blur5}學姐和仁學長而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.58,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把櫻花莊看得如此重要 我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是啊 沒有必要犧牲自己到這種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不是那樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說的我好像人很好一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是 把很多事當作了藉口而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「因為櫻花莊正值危機」也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「要考慮真白的心情」也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就連「不能在上井草學姐和三鷹學長面前不能哭」也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些全部都是藉口！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好害怕 一想到兩年的努力全部白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我就把櫻花莊 真白 還有學長學姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}作為最和情理的辯解準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}僅僅是為了不讓自己受傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是為了裝作沒有受傷 而利用了這些事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別說什麼你很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些根本不是溫柔 不是出於好意！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肯定是出於好意啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我受到了青山的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多虧了青山 我才能努力至今
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正因為青山在這裡 我才能堅持參與簽名活動至今
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這些都是託了青山的福！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以已經可以了 青山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼可能會可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼可能夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夠了！別再去想些多餘的事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我最差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經夠了 已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好好面對甄選的結果 別再逃避了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山想說什麼我都會聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的這兩年究竟算什麼 一直忍耐到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}朋友邀請我一起購物一起唱卡啦OK的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有出去玩過一次 沒有放鬆過一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全都是為了事後不後悔而努力至今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用錢方面一直很節儉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道 我全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很想去玩的 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明明把一切都獻出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是這些都沒有意義 毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一旦落選了就全白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告訴我 告訴我啊 神田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的這兩年究竟算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼沒有通過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼我就不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山已經很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比任何人都努力 是全世界最努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山真的已經很努力了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大哭了一場臉都花了 別總看我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}臉都花了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是很醜的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全沒有那種事 倒不如說很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不… 抱歉 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓人這麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看你們還有閒情在這打情罵俏應該是沒什麼問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}37.3° 微燒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給你藥 吃下去就趕緊睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是簽名活動還…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天是最後一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就趕緊休息一下 為了最後的衝刺做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是發著燒的孩子不能參加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？ 我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要神田陪睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那想讓他做些什麼就自己開口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 神田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在我睡著之前能在身邊陪著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會一直陪到你睡醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到睡著為止就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不許看我的睡相哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不看怎麼知道你有沒有睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也對 還真是個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不然我會胡思亂想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}剛才聽說了標題審查會的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也沒能通過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 我光顧著自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然沒能通過 但我覺得認真去做了真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得落選了並不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 這是謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實一點都不好 很艱辛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果鬆開這口氣好像我也會哭出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的 感覺這種心情已經受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要再次去努力還需要勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為變成膽小鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是 暫時無法再努力下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以啊 現在先休息一會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好好休息一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山一直努力到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得能這樣休息一下是正好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今後的事 等恢復了精神再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在保持這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山一路跑到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}稍微停下歇一會兒肯定沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山肯定會沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 聽我說聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}僅僅今天一天就收集到53人的簽名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看啊～看啊～看啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘛 能做的都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說距離全校學生的三分之二還差那麼一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}根本不是差一點 還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒有竭盡所能 什麼也沒做到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼 為什麼不來叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田 別鬧別扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你和馬尾辮已經做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且 雖然對空太有些過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但不能讓青山一個人在那裡睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對於現在的她而言 是需要共犯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你了 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山同學她還在保健室？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我們去接七海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小真白 空太就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.88,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還要多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還要收集多少人的才可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊 那就再多收集一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名 已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那種事是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太是騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有騙你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還沒有集齊啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明櫻花莊就要消失了 卻還沒有收集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\p1\fscx200\fscy250\bord0\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&HC1C1C1&)\pos(1130,930)\frz35.41}m 0 0 b 216 0 434 0 650 0 b 650 133 650 266 650 399 b 434 399 216 400 0 400
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.96,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\fs42\blur1\bord0\shad0\c&H8B857C&\frz36.62\pos(207.996,330.333)}教務主任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.96,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\frz37.12\blur1\bord0\shad0\c&H888278&\u1\pos(436,269)\fs45}由於千石老師是椎名真白的表親。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.96,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\frz36.91\blur1\bord0\shad0\c&H888278&\u1\fs45\pos(538.667,297)}所以至今我們一直尊重千石老師的意見、
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.96,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\frz37.1\blur1\bord0\shad0\c&H888278&\u1\fs45\pos(466.667,446.334)}盡可能地溫和地解決事情。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.96,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\blur1\bord0\shad0\c&H888278&\u1\fs42\pos(700,354.333)\frz38.04}但是隨著連載的繼續、這樣下去如果椎名真白的名字被
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.96,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\blur1\bord0\shad0\c&H888278&\u1\fs45\frz38.06\pos(748.001,410.332)}世人注意到 那麼讓椎名在此就讀的本校的立場就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要舉辦「聯署簽名活動辛苦了and畢業典禮前夜祭火鍋party」囉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事到如今還想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本次 於Rhythm Battler中見識到您精美的插畫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望椎名真白閣下能為敝公司的作品進行角色設計
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}追加的插畫 也可以拜託她來畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果能拜託她來畫 這份存在感一定能在審查會上推波助瀾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈哈 原來是這樣 來這一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這世間 還真是不合理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正凡人不論做些什麼都只是白費力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.74,0:21:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論多想追上去 最終都只能以失敗告終
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即使我們努力到片體鱗傷 反正也只是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}努力根本得不到回報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部都是如此 櫻花莊的事情也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不管多麼努力 我們都無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:58.67,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}ありふれた感情から
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:58.67,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}那些紛紛擾擾的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:02.30,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}卒業もできてなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:22:02.30,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}至今無法從中畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:05.47,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}眠れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:05.47,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}輾轉難眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:09.05,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}突然の雨抜かるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:09.05,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}不經意間突然下起大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.76,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}あの靴は瞬きする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.76,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}那雙鞋子隨之開始閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:19.15,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}君の世界をきっと受け止めている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:19.15,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}一定正在接受你整個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:22.52,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}君のリアル 僕の視線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:22.52,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}你的現實 我的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:25.82,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}どこが違うと知っても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:25.82,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}就算明白有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:32.78,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}あのくだびれたTシャツみたいにさせないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:32.78,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}也不會讓其變得跟那條破舊的T恤一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:34.37,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Prime number
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:34.37,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Prime number
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:40.13,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}世界にどれひとつとして同じものがない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:40.13,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}世界上不存在任何完全相同的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:46.67,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}心の空白を無理に塗れなくてもいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.13,0:22:46.67,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}所以無需強行塗滿心中的空白哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:54.14,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}たくさんの誰かの記憶に残されているよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:54.14,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}比起在許多人的心中留下回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:23:01.19,NCED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}屋根の上君だけの空になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.14,0:23:01.19,NCED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}我更喜歡成為只屬於你的屋上青空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會保護好櫻花莊的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「真白」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在大家的面前無法好好地叫出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:39.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs42\alpha&H00&\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\shad0\blur4\3c&H00BAFF&\4c&H26BBAF&\pos(665.133,446.2)}22 那閃耀的每一天飛馳而過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是不是在無意中抵制著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但 那一定是…
